Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar masu sa ido sun samu labarin cewa wasu manyan kwamandojin kungiyar IS biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, sun isa Afghanistan kwanan nan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya.
