Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya zargi sakatariyar yada labaran fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany da damun kafafen yada labarai ta hanyar mayar da rahotanninta na siyasa maimakon bayanai - da alama ta manta cewa manema labarai ne ke zabar tambayoyin.
Wata kasida da kamfanin dillancin labarai na AP, wanda shi ne kamfanin dillancin labarai mafi girma a Amurka, ya wallafa a ranar Asabar, ta ce taron manema labarai na fadar White House na iya zama "wata al'ada da aka karya", saboda McEnany ta mayar da shi "tallace-tallace mai inganci ga shugaban da ke fuskantar sake zabe, wurin da ake kai hare-hare kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma dandalin da ke da karancin bayanai" game da abin da gwamnati ke yi.
