Abin da kamfanin dillancin labarai na AP ya kasa ambata shi ne cewa da wuya a nemi wani sabon bayani a taron manema labarai.
'Yan jarida suna yawan amfani da manema labarai na Fadar White House don jawo hankalin kansu, wani nau'i na fasaha da Jim Acosta na CNN ya kammala.
Sun wuce dangantakar abokantaka ta kafofin watsa labarai da gwamnati, suna maimaita juna a cikin tambayar tambayoyin da aka yi da nufin kawai su zargi Shugaba Donald Trump.
A wasu lokuta, suna gabatar da kansu a matsayin labarai, kamar lokacin da wakiliyar CBS News Weijia Jiang ta mayar da martani ga "tambayar China" daga Trump ta hanyar yin nuni da wariyar launin fata: "Sir, me yasa kake fadin hakan musamman a gare ni?"
