A watan da ya gabata ne aka zabi jami'in diflomasiyyar Turkiyya Volkan Bozkir a matsayin shugaban babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya karo na 75, kuma an shirya zai isa birnin Islamabad a ranar Lahadi.
