Ted Cruz ya ce manufofin Pelosi su ne "samar da tsabar kudi a kan matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka"
Washington - Sanata Ted Cruz na jam'iyyar Republican daga Texas ya zargi kakakin majalisar wakilai Nancy Pelosi da 'yan majalisar wakilai na jam'iyyar Democrat da tura wani kunshin tallafin cutar coronavirus wanda ya mayar da hankali kan "kashe kudi a kan matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka" yayin da ake ci gaba da tattaunawa kan mataki na gaba.
A wata hira da aka yi da shi a shirin "Face the Nation" a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar na fuskantar matsaloli biyu a lokaci guda: annobar da ta lakume rayukan mutane sama da 600,000 a fadin duniya da kuma "babban bala'i na tattalin arziki" a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wacce ta bayyana a shirin "Face the Nation" a gaban sanatan, "ba ta mayar da hankali kan ko daya daga cikin wadannan ba".
"Manufarta ita ce ta tara kudade a kan matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka", in ji dan jam'iyyar Republican na Texas.
"Kuma musamman, ka dubi $3 tiriliyan lissafin ta ke kokarin tura, shi ne kawai shoveling kudi don ta abokai da kuma ba a zahiri warware matsalar. Our haƙiƙa ya kamata Amirkawa so don samun koma aiki. Suna so su iya samar da su iyali. "
'Yan Republican a majalisar dattawa da fadar White House sun kwashe makon da ya gabata suna tattaunawa kan sharuddan mataki na hudu na yaki da cutar coronavirus, wanda suke sa ran zai lakume dala tiriliyan daya.
A karshen mako, shugaban ma'aikatan fadar White House Mark Meadows da sakataren baitulmalin Amurka Steven Mnuchin sun koma Capitol Hill don ci gaba da tattaunawa da ma'aikatan majalisar dattawa, kuma Mnuchin ya shaida wa Fox News a wata hira a ranar Lahadi cewa shugaban masu rinjaye na majalisar dattawa Mitch McConnell zai bayyana cikakkun bayanai a ranar Litinin.
Batun da ya fi daukar hankalin 'yan majalisar wakilai - kuma wani batu na takaddama tsakanin 'yan Republican da 'yan Democrat - shi ne batun karin tallafin rashin aikin yi, wanda ya fara karewa a karshen makon nan.
Yayin da 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat ke son shirin "mataki na hudu" na coronavirus ya ci gaba da karin dala 600 ga amfanin, 'yan jam'iyyar Republican suna kira da a rage shi kuma suna jayayya cewa wasu Amurkawa sun fi samun kudi daga rashin aikin yi fiye da yadda suke samu a albashi.
